        <abstract>
            <p>CD’s illness: he is vomiting "vegetable" cells.</p> 
<p>Dutrochet has published the best of CD’s observations on tendrils [see <hi rend="italic">Climbing plants</hi>, p. 1 n.].</p> 
            <p>Lyell has found Joshua Trimmer’s Arctic shells on Moel Tryfan.</p>
